/*! PhotoSwipe Default UI CSS by Dmitry Semenov | photoswipe.com | MIT license */
/*

	Contents:

	1. Buttons
	2. Share modal and links
	3. Index indicator ("1 of X" counter)
	4. Caption
	5. Loading indicator
	6. Additional styles (root element, top bar, idle state, hidden state, etc.)

